# Exploration: fmt

## Rounds
  round 0: 32 isolated cumulative, 12 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 32 isolated cumulative, 12 identical in round (refinement)

## Distinguished: 7/7 flags
  7 solo (unique behavior)
  1 behavioral aliases detected

Aliases: -c = --crown-margin, -g = --goal, -p = --prefix, -s = --split-only, -t = --tagged-paragraph, -u = --uniform-spacing, -w = --width

## Solo (unique behavior)
  -c  # preserve indentation of first two lines
  -g  # goal width (default of 93% of width)
  -p  # reformat only lines beginning with STRING,
  -s  # split long lines, but do not refill
  -t  # indentation of first line different from second
  -u  # one space between words, two after sentences
  -w  # maximum line width (default of 75 columns)

